OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,FA group of Belfast city centre
OL,7,Fresidents have called for short term
OL,8,Fholiday lets to be banned.
OL,10,FThey've raised concerns that their
OL,11,Fresidential areas are turning into
OL,12,Fparty zones which are causing the
OL,13,Fdownfall of the community.
OL,15,FPeople living around the City centre
OL,16,Fclaim there's now a high number of
OL,17,Fhouses which were once home to long-
OL,18,Fterm residents being rented out to
OL,19,Fpeople visiting Belfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
