FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,FResident Una McNulty said: "Within a 5-
OL,7,Fminute walking radius, there are 16
OL,8,Fshort-term holiday lets in this area.
OL,9,FAnd of those 16, there's only one that
OL,10,Fhas planning permission and there's
OL,11,Fonly five that are certified with
OL,12,FTourism NI."
OL,14,FThis is primarily a residential area
OL,15,Fwith people living here for
OL,16,Fgenerations. Maureen was born in the
OL,17,Ffront room of her house and has lived
OL,18,Fhere all her life.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,FMaureen McMahon said: "We've had times
OL,7,Fon the other end of this row where
OL,8,Fthere've been parties.
OL,10,F"They've been told by their next-door
OL,11,Fneighbour, actually, that they were
OL,12,Fhere to have a party, with no
OL,13,Fconsideration for anyone else who has
OL,14,Fto get up for work in the morning
OL,15,Fbecause this can go on till 2:00 and
OL,16,F3:00 in the morning."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,FShe continued: "There's also an
OL,7,Fextension at the back of the house
OL,8,Fdown the street, where the party's
OL,9,Fbeen seen on top of the extension with
OL,10,Ftheir bottles of beer or whatever it
OL,11,Fis that they're drinking.
OL,13,F"This has been a very close community.
OL,14,FWe all look after each other, but now
OL,15,Fas a result of this... it's actually
OL,16,Fcausing the downfall of the community."
OL,18,FDamien was kept up and awake all night
OL,19,Fafter the house next door had noisy
OL,20,Fpeople staying for the night.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,FResident Damien told UTV that "you
OL,7,Fjust don't know when it's going to
OL,8,Fhappen."
OL,10,FHe continued: "Maybe you're having
OL,11,Ftrouble sleeping at night as it is,
OL,12,Fespecially with the hot weather.
OL,14,F"So once you ever do, you know, you do
OL,15,Froll over, and then, you know, a few
OL,16,Fhours later you've got music,
OL,17,Fshouting, screaming, banging.
OL,19,F"Thin walls as well in these
OL,20,Fresidential areas.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,F"It's tough, it is just tough.
OL,8,F"That has a knock-on effect on your
OL,9,Fweek, you know, whereas these guys
OL,10,Fjust go, 'Well, I can sleep in till
OL,11,Fabout sort of 10:00 or 11:00. Next day
OL,12,FI'm up and away,' and no
OL,13,Frepercussions, you know?"
OL,15,FA concern for many residents is that
OL,16,Fthere isn't much parking for those who
OL,17,Flive all year round.
OL,19,FWhen some of the houses have multiple
OL,20,Fresidents visiting for the night,
OL,21,Fparking becomes even more difficult.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,FOfficial figures from Tourism NI show
OL,7,Fthere are nearly 1,000 self-catering
OL,8,Funits registered with nearly 3,000 bed
OL,9,Fspaces in Belfast alone.
OL,11,FTourism legislation does not give any
OL,12,Fpowers to control or cap the number of
OL,13,Fproperties, but residents here want
OL,14,Fthe Assembly to make a bold
OL,15,Flegislative change.
OL,17,FUna McNulty said: "I want them banned
OL,18,Fcompletely.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784922490
OL,3,CCity centre residents call for ban on
OL,4,Cshort term holiday lets
OL,6,F"If we look at what's happening in the
OL,7,Frest of Europe, it's actually
OL,8,Fimpossible to enforce legislation.
OL,10,F"So you have areas in Spain that are
OL,11,Flooking to ban them and have them
OL,12,Fbanned by 2028.
OL,14,F"We have to learn from what happened
OL,15,Fin other countries."
OL,17,FWith the summer season underway and
OL,18,Fthe influx set to commence in the
OL,19,Fcoming weeks, residents are fearful
OL,20,Fthey may see an increase in
OL,21,Fdisturbances.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
